{"tid":2238563,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"紅磡站停車場男子高處墮下亡","createTime":"2020-10-11T08:48:10.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-11T11:16:46.000Z","uid":240362,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"ad3ad449aa3df279388fa546a71ee0ec38b6d8b0","tid":2238563,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-11T08:48:10.000Z","msg":"今日(11日)下午3時許，港鐵紅磡站多層停車場發生墮樓事件，一名男子被發現由上址高處墮下，跌落地下通道重傷昏迷，職員發現報警，救護員到場證實男子明顯死亡，毋須送院。警員到場登樓調查，於停車場6樓檢獲1張圓櫈、一枝拐杖及一對黑色皮鞋，懷疑男事主站於櫈上攀越欄河後墮樓，正調查男子墮樓原因，初步相信案件無可疑。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nSOURCE: 東網"},{"pid":"169a148a91e28fa5398af2fcf258196675c3f21d","tid":2238563,"uid":192409,"like":6,"dislike":17,"score":-11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-11T08:49:00.000Z","msg":"手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2584fdfbf17b73b447008a1b8a8f24d426b41921","tid":2238563,"uid":201359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-11T08:51:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00bc22f303669acd4f78d0f25e3cf5ddab8f5997","tid":2238563,"uid":212623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-11T08:52:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5ff727339e3c8dc1a54c7c731a6c1af9ab6c014","tid":2238563,"uid":8500,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-11T08:52:49.000Z","msg":"又係黑色<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"692c4242dff635bf71d0353efe3e6195a4423d33","tid":2238563,"uid":289946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-11T08:53:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85f85cdbcc5537631f7bc851088cd